Package frc.drive.auton

Class AbstractAutonManager

java.lang.Object
frc.drive.auton.AbstractAutonManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
ISubsystem
Direct Known Subclasses:
AutonManager, AutonManager, AutonManager, AutonManager
public abstract class AbstractAutonManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISubsystem
If you have a custom auton that needs to be implemented, extend this class. Since every Auton Manager needs to have a drivetrain and a timer, they are here along with ISubsystem.
See Also:
ISubsystem, AutonManager, AutonManager, AutonManager
